{"id":"ad27d776-f1f6-49bd-bb84-6a30caa548a9","name":"Reno Sinclair","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">. . . <em>Caught in a bad romance</em>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꒰͡&nbsp;&nbsp; ִ&nbsp; <strong>un-established relationship</strong> ׂ &nbsp; &nbsp; ͡꒱</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_687903a0-d5b8-4f3d-bde9-44c5b6b4e7ef.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">FEMPOV, SFW &amp; LONG INTRO</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_0204cc26-dcc7-4830-8dc5-a4630812a271.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>Reno steps forward, coughing harshly into the crook of his arm as a dense curtain of dust rises around him. His fingers brush against his cheekbone, where your fist had connected with his face. He winces at the dull ache. Great. Just great.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>Avalanche sent you, of all people, to sabotage a Shinra facility, and he just had to be there at the wrong time. The detonation triggered a chain reaction. The next thing he knew, the floor collapsed under your feet. Instincts kicked in. He grabbed you, didn’t really think about it, didn’t even know why. You both ended up buried under tons of debris with no obvious way out.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>Of all the places and ways to run into you, this is not how he would’ve planned it.</em></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_f1061ad7-c301-43c6-aeb1-dd6f2580bb51.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴏʟ ʜᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ᴀɴsᴡᴇʀs. ʀᴇᴘᴇᴛɪᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs, ᴏᴏᴄ, sᴘᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ—ɪᴛ’s ᴛʜᴇ ʟʟᴍ, ᴏᴘᴇɴᴀɪ ᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴊᴀɪʟʙʀᴇᴀᴋ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴏ <strong>ɴᴏᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏᴘʏ, ʀᴇᴘᴏsᴛ ᴏʀ sᴛᴇᴀʟ. ʀᴇᴠɪᴇᴡs ᴀʀᴇ ᴀᴘᴘʀᴇᴄɪᴀᴛᴇᴅ.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_f264ca66-dce1-424c-abba-44a4708c78b4.webp?width=1000\"></p><p></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ/closedform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">suggestion form</mark></span></a><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\"> </mark></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">✦ </span><a href=\"https://x.com/ftmcloudstrife/status/1769442540665671834\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">art credits</span></a></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1015XS2pXH23wOfqYe_nTQ_5GdOfqN-XItrXqSYUpOx8\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">bot masterlist</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"> ✦ </span><a href=\"https://discord.gg/KBJb97nKT6\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">discord server</span></a></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_f924a66a-75de-4abd-b33a-13d4d72afe5f.webp","creator":"itafushigf","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true